        <item>
          <title>Private Lunar Lander Fails After Landing Sideways on Moon</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A private lunar lander has failed after landing sideways in a crater near the moon's south pole, ending its mission. The lander, named Athena, was launched by Texas-based Intuitive Machines and carried tens of millions of dollars' worth of experiments.]]></description>
